divs: Sighting DetailsI was sitting in my back yard, after doing the Cseti protocols (earlier in the day ) from Dr. Steven Greer, when I noticed a satelite moving accross a star, just after it crossed the star the star got real bright, then it MOVED!! to its left i followed it a little while then it went out of view. it happened in San Jacinto, Calif. August 1st 2009 around 8 to 9 pm
Summary: Star got bright then moved off to its left my right.
trends: There have been 6 other sightings in San Jacinto
There were no other sightings in San Jacinto on or around August 1st 2009
